Do not treat all sources equally
Use the following priority:

target runtime compatibility
current repo conventions
legacy system behavior
PDFs for game intent / terminology


If two sources conflict, prefer the one higher in the list
If the legacy system and current module disagree, explain the difference before coding
If PDFs and existing code disagree, identify whether the difference is a bug, a simplification, or a migration gap
